    seoDescription: "How to source shorts from Pakistan — inseam lengths, fabric options, waistband specification, custom branding and certification for retail and brand buyers.",
    keywords: ["shorts manufacturer Pakistan", "chino shorts supplier Pakistan", "swim shorts OEM Pakistan", "athletic shorts Pakistan"],
