    category: "Woven Garments Sourcing",
    title: "Sourcing Shorts from Pakistan: Inseam Lengths, Fabric & Custom Branding",
    description: "A sourcing guide for shorts from Pakistan — fabric selection by type (chino, linen, swim, active), inseam length specification, waistband and lining options, custom branding and certification requirements for retail, beach and athletic buyers.",
